{"tid":411993,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"optimistic nihilism(樂觀虛無主義) 一齊嚟傾下生命嘅意義","createTime":"2017-09-24T09:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T00:44:15.000Z","uid":25759,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18dd735a091051fefd8a82ed0a3141dee6815cea","tid":411993,"uid":25759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MBRqu0YOH14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMBRqu0YOH14&d=gvPQCd7LuzKh4Sy6KYKq1Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8e0bfdc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MBRqu0YOH14</a><br />\n唔知有冇人睇過呢條片 真係好正 唔單只簡單介紹晒optimistic nihilism嘅內容而且畫面都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係in a nutshell呢個channel最好睇嘅片<br />\n<br />\n呢個樂觀虛無主義亦都好似荒謬主義(absurdism) 簡單黎講就係生命本來就冇意義 人應該接受呢個事實 有咁開心就生活得咁開心<br />\n<br />\n仲有另一個對生命意義嘅解釋都好有趣 就係存在主義(existentialism) 大概係講世界嘅存在冇意義 但係我地可以靠自己創造同賦予生命意義<br />\n但其實我都唔係非常理解存在主義 要講亦都實在有太多同太複雜 我只係志在睇下大家有咩睇法同埋想介紹好片 有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64693006bf60d9f929228d78efe1dd9bfac2fed5","tid":411993,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇完卡謬既書對存在主義好有興趣"},{"pid":"36eb67510eb9ee80e7fcbdcec2b7767cd22a0222","tid":411993,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"咁同存在主義有咩分別？"},{"pid":"767719df75fafe4af5e12e2d3d34be50ae5d9618","tid":411993,"uid":138502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"哲學角度﹕卡謬談自殺 在荒謬中安頓自己<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20160925/s00005/1474740098977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160925%2Fs00005%2F1474740098977&d=gvPQCd7LuzKh4Sy6KYKq1Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=67908e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160925%2Fs00005%2F1474740098977&h=efce02f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20160925/s00005/1474740098977</a>"},{"pid":"4fa0748230090ead8981078946367c64403ee169","tid":411993,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁同存在主義有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n一個可以靠自己創造同賦予生命意義.<br />\n一個認為任何野都係虛無 (就算自己賦予既意義亦都冇意義)"},{"pid":"a2d2f4a64c896518170eb4dcafc2c73d88f843d5","tid":411993,"uid":102178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T21:01:26.000Z","msg":"留個名"},{"pid":"b0d01237758ab1dc51fb24d0fbe3fe2cf2b86ff7","tid":411993,"uid":14046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T21:49:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a660674b1a394f901d21414c0c61a07b86a559f3","tid":411993,"uid":149448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:51:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"06809e66c044e418ab53b50dbb3461a6ceeec121","tid":411993,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:54:33.000Z","msg":"Kurzgesagt?"},{"pid":"407f7e205b92a45b10d46880edfc08f45a5ce0ea","tid":411993,"uid":131012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebf2df8cf38f3bf3f132de9d3a093767485db90","tid":411993,"uid":97299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}